text:
Jeremy Phillip Felton (born 17 July 1987) is an American R&B and hip hop music singer, songwriter, rapper, and record producer from Illinois. He plays the vocals, piano, percussion, bass guitar and saxophone. He has worked with other artists like 50 Cent, Hitmaka, PartyNextDoor and Ty Dolla Sign.
Solo singles.
